      Quake III Arena Version 1.32 (the lastest point release) with osp and cpma mod

   1. Unrar Quake III Arena 1.32.rar with WinRAR or some other prog.
   2. Start quake3.exe
   3. If you want to play the osp mod or cpma mod, make a new shortcut on your desktop, 
      and put +set fs_game osp/cpma after it like this for example:
      &quot;C:Program FilesGamesQuake III Arena 1.32quake3.exe&quot; +set fs_game osp
      You can also select the mods from the quake main menu but this is faster.
   4. You can install MAXBrowse 1.2 to browse quake3 servers if you like.
   5. There&amp;#039;s a keygen included, but you don&amp;#039;t need it until u get invalid cdkey
      or mis-typed cdkey errors in some servers when trying to connect.

P.S. If you enter a server and you are forced to spec by pb, go to the pb folder
     and run pbweb.exe so punkbuster will be updated to the latest version.
